00}}$ =\n($8.05\\pm1.15$)$\\times$10$^{11} \\rm{M_\\odot}$ with a corresponding radius of\n$R_{\\rm{200}}$ = $192.37\\pm9.24$ kpc and a local dark matter density of\n$0.39\\pm0.03$ GeV cm$^{-3}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Dec 2022 16:21:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-12"}
