nthe THDM+triplet, as the previous case. Among all the possibilities, we call\nthe attention to one special case which generates the 3HDM+triplet scenario.\nFor the last case, when lepton number is violated at high energy scale, the\nsextet become very massive and decouples from the original scalar content of\nthe 3-3-1 model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Dec 2022 18:50:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-21"}
