riate WKB double-scaling regime, which is captured by the refined\ntopological string in the Nekrasov-Shatashvili limit.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Dec 2022 19:23:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Mar 2023 17:26:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-30"}
