ratures. In an applied magnetic\nfield the magnetization process features plateaus and jumps in a wide range of\n$J_2/J_1$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Dec 2022 08:26:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-22"}
