 schemes. In\naddition to being a powerful tool for quantitative data analysis, it can also\nguide experimentalists in choosing appropriate sampling frequency (at least 20\nmeasured points per single characteristic period) and length of the measured\ntrajectories (at least 10 periods) to estimate the force field and\nenvironmental characteristics with a desired accuracy and precision.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Dec 2022 09:30:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-02"}
